Comment: 0,0:01:09.17,0:01:14.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}真実は何処へ　探して
Comment: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:16.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Where's my soul?
Comment: 0,0:01:25.69,0:01:27.94,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}It's like a fear　悪い夢の様で
Comment: 0,0:01:28.02,0:01:30.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}目覚めても　All I've got is bones
Comment: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:32.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}I'm in a panic? Get out, hurry
Comment: 0,0:01:32.69,0:01:35.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Oh, there're mysteries and miseries
Comment: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:37.99,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Dead or alive　狭間に揺られて
Comment: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:40.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}彷徨えば　Right to left to hell
Comment: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:42.79,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}孤独の招待　感情の消退
Comment: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:45.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}踊る1 2 3 steps on this dark stage
Comment: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:47.62,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Raise your flag, march on, fight
Comment: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:51.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}仮面の淵へ　手を掛けどただ骨が鳴るのみ
Comment: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:53.38,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Wars and swords, tears and blood
Comment: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:58.26,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}溢る力が　不意に嗤い出した
Comment: 0,0:01:58.55,0:02:03.97,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}真実は何処へ　探して
Comment: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:06.27,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Where's my soul? Where's my heart?
Comment: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:09.10,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}現実に呑まれてく
Comment: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:13.98,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Don't hesitate, go this way
Comment: 0,0:02:14.07,0:02:16.53,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}理解らない　構わない
Comment: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:19.49,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}紛い力振るっても
Comment: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:23.99,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}ただこの世界を生き抜けよ
Comment: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:29.29,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}嗚呼　失くした哀しみがまた疼いてく…
Comment: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:32.25,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Misery-World
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.17,0:01:14.72,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}真實在何處  我四處探尋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:16.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}我魂在何方
